{
  "stem": "6924.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She didn't like that idea because there wasn't too much room there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I insisted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And finally she gave in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We decided, first, they left for that place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "By that-- in the-- the place in the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the village was Uhorce.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, one day, the-- that [INAUDIBLE] came, and he took us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came with a-- with a buggy, and he took us over to the place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that place-- we-- we gave him some-- you know, we paid him every month.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We gave him some money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My aunt-- well, she was outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was hidden by somebody there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was-- she wasn't in the ghetto when it was-- when it was that-- the action was there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed by that [INAUDIBLE], by that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he treated us pretty good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I mean, there was-- there were people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were desperate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were very poor people, those [? guys. ?] And-- and the thing is, we paid them, and they couldn't even buy an extra piece of bread because it was a small village.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody knew somebody else's business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he would have showed-- anything that he's buying, anything extra, right away they would suspect that he's hiding Jews [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he-- he-- he was very careful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The conditions there, in that place, and that-- they made a-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Under the stable, he dig-- he digged-- made like a little room underground.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How big was it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was just enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just [INAUDIBLE] got-- just mostly-- you couldn't even get up altogether.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of the time, you had to sit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sit and-- and that's it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he brought us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He built this bunker, under--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he built it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
